nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 178 is the 156th issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the eighty-sixth issue published by Titan Magazines. It was released on January 16, 2018. This was the final Star Wars Insider issue to feature Will Salmon as editor.

Star Wars Insider #178 lifts the lid of secrecy on the next chapter in the Star Wars saga! Learn about the new stars, creatures and starships, plus continue the epic journey with Luke, Rey, Finn and Poe! Insider brings you the latest news, interviews photos and more!
